Thanks for the upload!  Hope it's a funny show.

This is exactly like Portland.  The actual mayor of Portland plays one of the assistants to the actor that plays the mayor..  Also, it really is the kind of place where people exchange their CDs for vinyl records.  I've seen a ton of people I know fill in as extras since Portland is big enough where it feels like a big city, but small enough to where you run into people you know all the time.  This show is hilarious.
